headline: Smurfit Westrock Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: DUBLIN, January 30, 2025-- Smurfit Westrock plc (NYSE:SW, LSE:SWR) (the "Company") announced today that its Board approved a quarterly dividend of $0.4308 per share on its ordinary shares. The quarterly dividend of $0.4308 per ordinary share is payable March 18, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on February 14, 2025.
